# 빌드: 저장소 루트에서 docker build -f Dockerfile.api .
# 실행 시 DATABASE_URL 등 환경변수 필요.
FROM node:22-alpine
WORKDIR /app
COPY package.json package-lock.json ./
COPY apps ./apps
COPY packages ./packages
RUN npm ci
RUN npm exec --workspace=@stock-monitoring/db -- prisma generate
ENV NODE_ENV=production
EXPOSE 4000
CMD ["npm", "run", "start", "-w", "@stock-monitoring/api"]
